item.title: CVE-2021-24513|2024-08-03T19:35:19.766Z -- unknown -- form%20builder%20%7C%20create%20responsive%20contact%20forms
item.description: The Form Builder | Create Responsive Contact Forms WordPress plugin before 1.9.8.4 does not sanitise or escape its Form Title, allowing high privilege users such as admin to set Cross-Site Scripting payload in them, even when the unfiltered_html capability is disallowed
